WEBVTT

00:09.999 --> 00:10.919
It's a good idea

00:11.519 --> 00:13.679
but it's not your usual approach.

00:14.439 --> 00:15.679
Which teacher taught you?

00:16.359 --> 00:16.960
Tell me.

00:19.080 --> 00:19.839
It was

00:21.239 --> 00:22.080
a female teacher.

00:22.839 --> 00:23.559
A female teacher?

00:24.199 --> 00:24.600
Who?

00:25.719 --> 00:26.239
So, who?

00:30.480 --> 00:31.519
Why aren't you answering?

00:31.960 --> 00:32.559
So secretive.

00:33.480 --> 00:34.519
Could it be your crush?

00:35.239 --> 00:36.120
No more wild guesses.

00:44.360 --> 00:46.800
Tell me which family she is from.

00:46.800 --> 00:48.400
I, Earl Yunyang, will go all out

00:48.400 --> 00:49.235
to be the matchmaker.

00:50.040 --> 00:51.000
Stop messing around.

00:51.800 --> 00:52.879
My mother is still ill.

00:53.319 --> 00:54.480
No nonsense in front of her.

00:56.760 --> 00:57.800
But if you ask me,

00:58.120 --> 00:58.919
don't you think

00:58.919 --> 01:00.240
you're overthinking this case?

01:01.040 --> 01:02.080
Your mother fell ill.

01:03.120 --> 01:05.120
My aunt, the empress,
and my uncle, the emperor,

01:05.640 --> 01:07.280
sent imperial physicians
to check on her.

01:07.280 --> 01:08.760
They're just as concerned as always.

01:09.000 --> 01:11.160
We have Official Wu
who is working to mediate things.

01:11.290 --> 01:13.720
Honestly, I think His Majesty
might scold him a bit at most.

01:14.519 --> 01:16.320
Duke of Ding won't be
in any serious trouble.

01:19.119 --> 01:20.000
I hope so.

02:41.700 --> 02:45.100
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Jiu Chong Zi" by Zhi Zhi)

02:45.100 --> 02:48.060
=Episode 6=

02:54.359 --> 02:55.720
Official Wu, please wait.

02:58.120 --> 03:00.360
I wasn't targeting you
in front of the emperor earlier.

03:00.600 --> 03:01.920
It's just that the emperor asked,

03:01.920 --> 03:03.879
I can only speak honestly.

03:06.280 --> 03:07.560
Honestly, huh?

03:08.400 --> 03:10.240
If it's for the court's stability,

03:10.240 --> 03:11.359
then it's all good.

03:12.000 --> 03:14.400
But this concerns major matters
in the southeast.

03:15.280 --> 03:17.800
It seem not to be related
to the Ministry of Rites now, does it?

03:20.570 --> 03:22.280
With the Dragon Boat Festival
approaching,

03:22.599 --> 03:27.680
why don't you go home
and rest for a few days?

03:31.320 --> 03:32.720
Since you've instructed me to do so,

03:32.720 --> 03:34.240
I can only comply.

03:51.359 --> 03:51.960
Mr. Wu,

03:53.520 --> 03:56.400
is this Official Dou
from the Western Dou Family?

03:56.400 --> 03:57.039
Yes.

03:58.180 --> 04:00.360
His Majesty read officials'
memorials against the Duke,

04:00.360 --> 04:02.599
then he asked
about Meisun's health instead.

04:03.400 --> 04:05.240
That shows he's worried, doesn't it?

04:05.879 --> 04:07.359
But Dou Shishu went on to say

04:07.359 --> 04:09.280
that bringing the Duke of Ding back
under arrest

04:09.599 --> 04:11.440
could destabilize the southeast.

04:11.759 --> 04:13.639
Isn't that like accusing Meisun

04:13.639 --> 04:16.400
of building up an army
to start a rebellion?

04:18.400 --> 04:20.520
Does Dou Shishu have a grudge
against Uncle?

04:20.520 --> 04:22.919
Dou Shishu has always been cautious
and low-profile,

04:22.919 --> 04:25.260
especially before he was promoted
to the Ministry of Rites.

04:25.280 --> 04:27.280
He has never crossed the line.

04:28.390 --> 04:30.379
It turns out,
he's just been hiding his ambition

04:30.939 --> 04:33.620
and coveting the vacant seats
of the Grand Secretariat.

04:34.180 --> 04:36.120
If Uncle is painted
as a treacherous minister,

04:36.459 --> 04:38.280
then Dou Shishu
who calls for his removal

04:38.459 --> 04:39.840
will naturally get the credit.

04:40.420 --> 04:41.819
Take good care of your mother.

04:42.339 --> 04:43.760
When Meisun arrives in the capital,

04:43.760 --> 04:45.960
the Grand Secretariat will have ways
to deal with this.

04:47.100 --> 04:47.920
Thank you, Mr. Wu.

04:53.780 --> 04:55.699
Have you tried
the Dou Family's rice dumpling?

04:56.660 --> 04:57.379
Rice dumplings?

04:58.259 --> 04:59.220
You must try it.

05:05.060 --> 05:06.120
If that's the case,

05:06.120 --> 05:08.780
then it must be Fourth Young Lady Dou who tipped off her uncle.

05:09.420 --> 05:10.379
That wicked woman.

05:11.339 --> 05:13.220
Earlier, you praised her
for being sharp,

05:13.420 --> 05:14.300
loyal, and kind.

05:15.660 --> 05:17.660
I... I'm terrible at judging people.

05:19.699 --> 05:21.400
If she's really targeting
the Duke of Ding,

05:21.620 --> 05:23.660
the Shadow Guard
would have wiped out Tan's Manor.

05:24.139 --> 05:25.459
But everything's fine over there,

05:25.459 --> 05:26.860
and the child is well taken care of.

05:27.259 --> 05:29.819
Also, General Yan is keeping
an eye on things.

05:31.180 --> 05:32.540
That just makes it even stranger.

05:32.710 --> 05:34.800
Fourth Young Lady Dou
has been living in seclusion.

05:34.939 --> 05:36.740
How would she know
all these court affairs?

05:38.379 --> 05:39.720
There's also another possibility.

05:39.939 --> 05:41.180
It's not just Dou Shishu.

05:41.459 --> 05:43.939
The entire Dou Family may be her pawns.

05:44.459 --> 05:46.680
She could be plotting
and manipulating people from afar.

05:47.459 --> 05:49.200
Then Young Lord has become her leverage

05:49.200 --> 05:49.860
to control us.

05:51.379 --> 05:52.740
If that's true,

05:52.939 --> 05:55.920
it's hard to believe someone as beautiful
as Fourth Young Lady Dou

05:55.920 --> 05:57.339
could be so ruthless.

06:00.180 --> 06:01.560
Uncle hasn't even arrived here yet,

06:01.560 --> 06:03.880
and we've already crossed paths
with the Dou Family twice.

06:04.139 --> 06:07.259
There's bound to be more conflict ahead.

06:08.499 --> 06:10.060
We have to figure out

06:10.740 --> 06:11.840
what they're really after.

06:17.139 --> 06:18.699
Xingyi suffered a lot in the past

06:19.899 --> 06:21.379
and ended up with rheumatism.

06:22.620 --> 06:25.139
That's why I sent over
some mugwort medicinal oil.

06:26.180 --> 06:27.819
It wasn't anything valuable.

06:28.579 --> 06:29.860
But he returned it to me.

06:31.019 --> 06:31.939
We're in-laws

06:32.740 --> 06:34.180
and serve the same court.

06:35.060 --> 06:36.600
Yet, the way he avoids any association,

06:36.600 --> 06:38.240
you'd think we were complete strangers.

06:40.499 --> 06:42.939
Father only didn't want
to give anyone an excuse to find fault

06:43.259 --> 06:44.699
and drag us into trouble.

06:45.060 --> 06:46.640
The Ministry of Rites keeps you busy.

06:46.640 --> 06:47.620
You rarely come home.

06:47.860 --> 06:49.740
Yet you still worry
about Father's health.

06:50.060 --> 06:51.480
I'm truly grateful, Fifth Brother.

06:51.540 --> 06:52.459
No need to thank me.

06:53.300 --> 06:54.180
We're family.

06:55.060 --> 06:56.499
I came back during my leave

06:56.780 --> 06:57.899
because there's something

06:58.100 --> 06:59.720
I need to discuss with you and Shiying.

06:59.899 --> 07:00.300
Sit.

07:01.660 --> 07:03.740
Ms. Longevity is 23 this year

07:04.379 --> 07:07.060
and Ming has turned 16 this year, right?

07:07.459 --> 07:08.060
Yes.

07:08.939 --> 07:09.939
If it were a boy,

07:10.660 --> 07:12.320
he'd be preparing
for the imperial exams.

07:12.330 --> 07:14.350
Not being able to leave an heir
for the Dou Family

07:14.360 --> 07:16.699
and making you worry about its future,

07:17.180 --> 07:18.680
it's my failure as a sister-in-law.

07:20.819 --> 07:23.379
This entire household runs
because of you.

07:24.019 --> 07:25.160
How could it be your fault?

07:25.579 --> 07:27.100
If anyone's at fault, it's Shiying.

07:27.300 --> 07:28.379
He may be an official.

07:28.660 --> 07:30.400
But he's driven by a set of principles.

07:31.100 --> 07:33.620
He's completely clueless
about the court's situation.

07:33.860 --> 07:35.960
If the Dou Family wants
to set a strong foothold,

07:37.259 --> 07:38.780
we can't do it alone.

07:39.420 --> 07:42.660
If Ming and Mr. Wu Shan's marriage
works out,

07:43.300 --> 07:45.420
the two families will be united

07:45.499 --> 07:46.819
and support each other.

07:47.180 --> 07:49.060
Honestly, they get along well.

07:49.259 --> 07:51.300
They're just a bit shy.

07:52.060 --> 07:52.860
In that case,

07:53.139 --> 07:55.400
invite Dezhen here
for the Dragon Boat Festival banquet.

07:55.660 --> 07:57.860
As elders,
we should do our part to help.

07:57.860 --> 07:59.899
All right, I'll send out
the invitation right away.

08:00.100 --> 08:02.459
Also, the Marquis of Jining
was in a mourning period.

08:03.139 --> 08:04.800
The three-year mourning period is over.

08:04.840 --> 08:07.780
It's time to address his and Ms. Longevity's
verbal engagement now.

08:07.960 --> 08:09.899
You should send out the invitation
for that too.

08:10.300 --> 08:11.980
I'll talk to Shiying about this.

08:12.740 --> 08:13.339
All right.

08:14.339 --> 08:17.339
The arrangement for Fifth Young Lady
and Mr. Wu Shan is a good thing.

08:18.100 --> 08:19.660
But Dou Zhao's childhood engagement

08:19.819 --> 08:21.379
had been long overdue.

08:21.499 --> 08:22.680
Why does Fifth Master seem

08:22.680 --> 08:24.339
to be interested in it again?

08:25.300 --> 08:26.780
He is not on leave.

08:27.300 --> 08:29.139
Father already sent word.

08:29.620 --> 08:31.180
Fifth Brother made a mistake in court

08:31.780 --> 08:32.980
and went against Official Wu.

08:33.180 --> 08:35.260
He was forced to take leave.

08:36.219 --> 08:37.339
Now,

08:37.339 --> 08:39.420
he's depending
on his two nieces' marriages.

08:39.819 --> 08:41.699
One is to aim for a powerful family.

08:42.020 --> 08:44.420
The other one is for a noble official.

08:44.660 --> 08:46.260
Isn't our Wang Family's connection

08:46.380 --> 08:47.380
not enough?

08:48.339 --> 08:50.219
My father is straightforward
and upright.

08:50.400 --> 08:52.600
He always does what's right,
not just favoring family.

08:52.739 --> 08:54.760
Now he wants a position
in the Grand Secretariat.

08:54.840 --> 08:56.979
Father won't want
to get involved in this mess.

08:58.180 --> 09:01.260
But if Dou Zhao
becomes Marchioness of Jining,

09:01.459 --> 09:03.380
won't she overshadow you?

09:05.099 --> 09:07.699
Wei Tingyu is famous for his extravagant
and careless lifestyle.

09:08.339 --> 09:10.739
Even though his family
has held the title for generations,

09:10.979 --> 09:12.219
they've spent all their wealth

09:12.219 --> 09:14.540
on funeral expenses in recent years.

09:16.020 --> 09:17.219
His sister, Wei Tingzhen,

09:17.619 --> 09:19.500
married the Duke of Jing
as his second wife.

09:20.579 --> 09:23.339
This whole family is driven by greed.

09:23.660 --> 09:25.859
They might be useful allies.

09:29.099 --> 09:30.140
Be careful, Madam.

09:31.099 --> 09:33.900
This butterfly loves
those silk tree flowers.

09:34.500 --> 09:36.420
Once their scale powder touched
the skin,

09:36.660 --> 09:38.060
the itch would be unbearable.

09:38.380 --> 09:39.660
I'll have the servant take care

09:39.660 --> 09:41.080
of all those butterflies right away.

09:43.219 --> 09:45.300
But they're so beautiful.

09:45.699 --> 09:47.200
Won't it be a pity to catch them all?

10:13.619 --> 10:14.939
Have a drink, Your Lordship.

10:24.900 --> 10:26.040
That's a wonderful painting.

10:26.459 --> 10:27.280
It's nicely painted.

10:27.280 --> 10:28.140
You're flattering me.

10:28.420 --> 10:29.800
You paint very well, Your Lordship.

10:39.339 --> 10:40.420
Your Ladyship,

10:41.020 --> 10:42.859
it's truly an honor to have you here.

10:44.540 --> 10:45.339
Where's the Marquis?

10:46.099 --> 10:46.900
He...

10:50.300 --> 10:51.739
Madam, wait.

10:52.420 --> 10:53.219
Excuse me, ladies.

10:53.979 --> 10:55.300
Madam, slowly.

10:55.300 --> 10:56.260
Watch your steps.

10:56.780 --> 10:58.140
Why don't you

10:58.140 --> 10:59.619
let me inform the Marquis first?

11:01.780 --> 11:04.020
Madam, please have mercy.

11:04.380 --> 11:05.780
If you barged in like this,

11:05.780 --> 11:07.420
the Marquis would beat me to death.

11:09.579 --> 11:11.380
Then I'll beat you foolish woman
to death now!

11:12.619 --> 11:13.260
Madam!

11:16.020 --> 11:16.619
Wonderful.

11:16.619 --> 11:17.459
Well painted.

11:19.780 --> 11:20.500
Peijin.

11:23.140 --> 11:23.859
Tingzhen?

11:29.900 --> 11:31.020
Fourth Young Lady Dou?

11:31.260 --> 11:32.420
Why her again?

11:32.979 --> 11:34.260
I've heard something reliable.

11:34.470 --> 11:36.240
(Wei Tingzhen, Duchess of Jing)
She's making

11:37.020 --> 11:38.500
at least this much in Futing now.

11:40.020 --> 11:41.579
But it's all just material stuff.

11:42.270 --> 11:44.120
Didn't Seventh Master Dou send
a letter earlier

11:44.180 --> 11:46.579
saying matters of marriage
should be left to fate?

11:46.660 --> 11:48.020
Doesn't that mean it's all over?

11:48.020 --> 11:49.020
Of course, not.

11:49.240 --> 11:51.120
Now the Dou Family
is taking the initiative,

11:51.120 --> 11:53.100
inviting us to join them
for the Festival outing.

11:55.420 --> 11:57.760
These past few years,
there have been disasters everywhere,

11:57.760 --> 11:59.300
and the harvest has been halved.

11:59.300 --> 12:01.560
But the expenses
at the household haven't dropped at all.

12:01.560 --> 12:02.579
Without anyone to help,

12:03.420 --> 12:04.760
do you know how much it costs

12:05.140 --> 12:06.760
to run the household?

12:07.339 --> 12:07.660
I...

12:07.660 --> 12:08.500
Just do as I say.

12:08.619 --> 12:10.099
Once Father's mourning period is over,

12:10.370 --> 12:12.120
we need to finalize
the marriage right away.

12:12.120 --> 12:12.859
But Tingzhen...

12:13.219 --> 12:14.850
The Dou Family's household
is in turmoil.

12:15.339 --> 12:16.819
She also grew up in the countryside.

12:17.180 --> 12:19.430
A young master who attended
their family's banquets said

12:19.660 --> 12:22.080
she doesn't care about the differences
between men and women,

12:22.080 --> 12:24.120
speaks disrespectfully,
and even argues with elders.

12:24.120 --> 12:25.339
She's completely uncouth.

12:27.380 --> 12:28.540
I was going to say

12:28.780 --> 12:30.800
that Dou Zhao is famous for her beauty.

12:30.800 --> 12:32.979
She's truly a stunning woman.

12:33.300 --> 12:34.819
Perhaps she could catch your eye?

12:36.900 --> 12:39.099
But since you seem
to dislike her so much,

12:39.380 --> 12:41.099
I won't worry
about your marriage anymore.

12:46.699 --> 12:47.420
Three.

12:48.180 --> 12:48.819
Two...

12:49.579 --> 12:50.020
Tingzhen,

12:54.140 --> 12:55.780
I'm a Marquis after all.

12:56.219 --> 12:58.260
So I should be more open-minded.

12:59.270 --> 13:01.040
Since we've already accepted
the invitation,

13:01.040 --> 13:03.300
it would be rude if we don't go.

13:03.900 --> 13:04.579
How about this?

13:05.500 --> 13:06.960
You can take charge of this.

13:12.180 --> 13:13.020
What a pity, really.

13:14.619 --> 13:15.420
One wrong stroke.

13:15.590 --> 13:17.640
Such a shame
for this winter plum blossom painting.

13:17.939 --> 13:18.699
Not at all.

13:20.520 --> 13:22.600
It's a beautiful painting
of the winter plum blossom.

13:22.600 --> 13:23.840
No, it's not a pity at all.

13:31.380 --> 13:32.600
Everyone, please take a look.

13:32.859 --> 13:35.060
"Who could have known
the winter's snow would come late,

13:35.060 --> 13:37.580
and a single winter plum blossom
would bloom out of the wall?"

13:37.580 --> 13:38.859
That's brilliant!

13:40.020 --> 13:40.579
Indeed.

13:45.579 --> 13:47.350
The tiger talisman
is something you can buy.

13:47.370 --> 13:49.600
Wang Yingxue only wants you
and Dou Ming to embroider it

13:49.600 --> 13:51.339
to torture your poor little fingers.

13:51.579 --> 13:52.099
Exactly.

13:52.500 --> 13:53.339
That's why

13:53.780 --> 13:55.939
I made sure to stitch it
all crooked and uneven.

13:56.459 --> 13:57.260
In any case,

13:57.420 --> 13:58.979
I should appear worse than Dou Ming.

13:59.380 --> 14:00.680
Are you downplaying yourself?

14:00.680 --> 14:01.660
Not entirely.

14:02.819 --> 14:05.859
The real trouble is asking you
to handle the banquet.

14:06.160 --> 14:09.060
Old Madam and Seventh Master Dou finally
managed to ease things up a bit.

14:09.060 --> 14:11.720
Now she's dragging a whole group
of people to join the festivities.

14:11.720 --> 14:13.580
I'm worried
it'll cause some misunderstandings.

14:13.580 --> 14:16.219
I don't think Wang Yingxue cares
about the festival at all.

14:16.280 --> 14:18.550
She just wants to set up
a marriage for you and Dou Ming.

14:21.900 --> 14:22.579
Young Lady,

14:23.219 --> 14:24.739
we got news from Zhaowen Bookstore.

14:43.300 --> 14:45.400
Wu Shan has been posted
as Assistant Director

14:45.400 --> 14:46.660
of Court of Imperial Sacrifices.

14:46.900 --> 14:48.979
I am fine with Wu Shan coming.

14:49.339 --> 14:50.459
But after six years,

14:50.459 --> 14:52.260
doesn't Wei Tingyu get the message?

14:52.660 --> 14:53.640
Why is he still coming?

14:53.680 --> 14:54.260
How shameless.

14:54.939 --> 14:55.579
Precisely.

14:56.699 --> 14:57.660
The physician said

14:57.900 --> 14:59.300
her days are numbered.

14:59.420 --> 15:00.339
Once she's gone,

15:00.660 --> 15:01.500
I will marry you.

15:04.579 --> 15:06.800
Song Mo is arrogant
due to his achievements and favor.

15:07.020 --> 15:10.219
He kidnapped and eloped
with Marchioness of Jining, Dou Zhao.

15:10.660 --> 15:11.540
Execute them

15:12.060 --> 15:13.060
to uphold the family law.

15:14.219 --> 15:15.900
This needs to be settled.

15:16.739 --> 15:18.040
I'll give him a proper welcome

15:18.579 --> 15:20.540
if he dares to show up.

15:27.739 --> 15:28.560
This way, please.

15:30.960 --> 15:32.200
The scenery here is beautiful,

15:32.200 --> 15:33.360
and the repairs are done well.

15:33.360 --> 15:35.040
As expected from the Cui Clan of Ji'an.

15:35.579 --> 15:37.939
Even a countryside manor
can have such elegance.

15:39.099 --> 15:42.060
My mother-in-law doesn't like
the bustling city.

15:42.619 --> 15:44.459
So she stays here to rest.

15:44.819 --> 15:47.939
Over the years,
all thanks to Zhao's company

15:48.140 --> 15:50.099
and her helping around the manor.

15:50.099 --> 15:51.699
I bet she's busy attending

15:51.699 --> 15:53.739
to my mother-in-law's afternoon nap now.

15:54.300 --> 15:55.780
I hope you won't mind

15:56.200 --> 15:57.640
she couldn't welcome you personally.

15:57.699 --> 16:01.520
Zhao is gentle, and virtuous,
and manages our household perfectly.

16:01.520 --> 16:02.420
Everyone who meets her

16:02.500 --> 16:04.339
has nothing but praise.

16:04.339 --> 16:06.180
Even her sisters

16:06.500 --> 16:07.739
are all kind and graceful,

16:08.180 --> 16:10.579
smart and composed.

16:19.300 --> 16:19.979
Oh, hello Uncle.

16:20.420 --> 16:22.420
Ru, what are you doing?

16:22.420 --> 16:25.260
I'll catch some more to add an extra dish
for tonight's banquet.

16:25.339 --> 16:25.939
Come on.

16:28.459 --> 16:29.060
I...

16:30.500 --> 16:31.699
Sorry about that.

16:31.699 --> 16:32.500
Ru takes

16:32.500 --> 16:34.300
after her father.

16:34.579 --> 16:35.540
She's a bit too lively.

16:36.260 --> 16:37.579
Come this way, please.

16:37.579 --> 16:38.819
Please come this way.

16:39.339 --> 16:40.180
Mr. Wu, this way.

16:40.260 --> 16:42.300
Aside from Ru,

16:42.300 --> 16:43.579
who's a bit energetic,

16:43.900 --> 16:46.739
the rest of the ladies
are all very quiet and graceful.

16:46.739 --> 16:47.260
I win!

16:47.859 --> 16:48.979
You lose again.

16:49.140 --> 16:50.140
Hurry up and pay up!

16:51.180 --> 16:52.500
Accept your defeat.

16:53.339 --> 16:54.619
Which tenant's daughter that?

16:54.619 --> 16:55.720
She's acting so rough.

16:55.720 --> 16:56.520
Chase her out now.

16:56.579 --> 16:57.380
Fifth Uncle!

16:57.699 --> 16:59.080
Let's play another round.

16:59.300 --> 17:01.020
It's me, Ansu.

17:01.459 --> 17:02.140
Ansu?

17:02.699 --> 17:04.219
Zhao taught me this game.

17:04.219 --> 17:05.220
It's so much fun!

17:05.460 --> 17:06.980
Do you want to play together?

17:08.379 --> 17:11.220
Miss Su is really good
at mental calculation.

17:11.540 --> 17:13.240
So it's no surprise she likes this game.

17:13.240 --> 17:15.099
Let's check out the backyard.

17:15.099 --> 17:15.700
Come with me.

17:18.740 --> 17:20.139
Come on, it's your turn now.

17:20.139 --> 17:20.940
Quickly.

17:20.940 --> 17:22.339
This courtyard

17:22.819 --> 17:24.220
is my mother-in-law's

17:24.220 --> 17:26.139
favorite courtyard.

17:26.899 --> 17:28.240
Look at these flowers and plants.

17:28.339 --> 17:31.220
They're carefully tended to every day.

17:34.700 --> 17:38.320
The courtyard is always green, with
birds chirping and flowers blooming.

17:38.320 --> 17:39.379
It's really lovely.

17:39.379 --> 17:40.460
There are more over there.

17:40.460 --> 17:41.899
Let's go and take a look.

17:42.139 --> 17:42.720
All right.

17:54.740 --> 17:55.460
Ming.

18:10.220 --> 18:12.260
As for Zhao, she's very quiet.

18:12.419 --> 18:15.060
Most of the time,
she writes and reads books.

18:15.360 --> 18:17.899
She's refined and graceful,
truly a woman of culture and virtue.

18:20.940 --> 18:21.540
Come.

18:22.659 --> 18:23.339
Ms. Longevity?

18:24.220 --> 18:25.500
That is very rude of you.

18:25.899 --> 18:28.480
I wanted to greet the guests
with this willow-shooting equipment.

18:29.339 --> 18:31.579
But my skills aren't great,

18:32.419 --> 18:34.220
and I ended up startling
our honored guests.

18:45.579 --> 18:47.520
It's perfect
that Fifth Master and Seventh Master

18:47.520 --> 18:49.350
are discussing official matters
in the study.

18:49.350 --> 18:50.840
With the two old scholars not around,

18:50.980 --> 18:52.980
the children would feel more at ease.

18:54.260 --> 18:56.980
I've heard the Dou Family's Madam Wang

18:57.099 --> 18:58.300
and Fourth Young Lady Dou

18:58.300 --> 18:59.819
are both quite skilled at making money.

19:00.260 --> 19:01.579
Madam Wang,

19:01.819 --> 19:03.379
you've helped many officials

19:03.379 --> 19:04.700
become rich.

19:04.700 --> 19:07.160
Seventh Master Dou marrying so well

19:07.160 --> 19:09.440
means his official career
will surely go smoothly.

19:09.440 --> 19:11.000
I don't deserve such compliments.

19:11.099 --> 19:12.379
I only make a small profit

19:12.379 --> 19:13.579
to support the household.

19:14.460 --> 19:17.339
It's Zhao who is truly extraordinary.

19:17.540 --> 19:19.300
She comes from wealth

19:19.300 --> 19:21.200
and is remarkably talented
at managing manors.

19:21.379 --> 19:23.460
She's already one of the richest
in the region.

19:25.419 --> 19:28.500
It's a pity that she doesn't trust me
as the matron of the household.

19:29.339 --> 19:31.500
If she would invest with me,

19:31.819 --> 19:35.260
I could guarantee her a 30% profit
in just half a year.

19:36.579 --> 19:39.260
If you make this marriage happen,

19:39.460 --> 19:44.020
I'd be happy to contribute 40%...

19:44.300 --> 19:45.579
No, I mean 50% of her dowry

19:45.980 --> 19:47.500
for you to manage.

19:49.540 --> 19:51.260
You're too kind.

19:51.740 --> 19:53.899
If we happen to become in-laws,

19:54.099 --> 19:56.060
there's no need
to mention helping or not.

19:56.220 --> 19:57.500
We're not outsiders here.

19:57.980 --> 19:59.500
Have some tea.

19:59.780 --> 20:00.339
Sure.

20:02.300 --> 20:04.740
What's the fun of shooting willow?

20:05.500 --> 20:07.179
(I knew your archery skills
are terrible)

20:07.360 --> 20:08.800
(and care so much about your face.)

20:09.060 --> 20:11.320
(If I made you think
we don't have the same interests)

20:11.419 --> 20:12.800
(and angry out of embarrassment,)

20:12.800 --> 20:15.560
(maybe you'd call off the engagement.
Now, that's the fun part!)

20:15.560 --> 20:16.339
What are those?

20:17.500 --> 20:19.020
A small gift from my elder sister.

20:19.500 --> 20:20.700
It's a kite soaring in the sky,

20:20.819 --> 20:22.500
symbolizing good fortune.

20:22.859 --> 20:24.540
"Look far to see a thousand li ahead,

20:24.780 --> 20:25.980
rising to new heights."

20:26.899 --> 20:28.120
Madam Wei is so thoughtful.

20:28.320 --> 20:30.520
Are these for Fifth Master Dou
and Seventh Master Dou?

20:35.300 --> 20:36.339
Madam Wang, take a look.

20:37.500 --> 20:39.220
"A fresh start leads

20:39.540 --> 20:41.179
to soaring heights."

20:41.460 --> 20:42.460
What a fine verse.

20:42.819 --> 20:44.320
Even the sentiment is wonderful.

20:44.320 --> 20:46.260
I had Peijin inscribe it personally.

20:46.500 --> 20:49.179
I wish him a bright future,

20:49.200 --> 20:51.339
a harmonious and happy life,
and soaring high together

20:51.619 --> 20:52.840
with Fourth Young Lady Dou.

20:55.819 --> 20:57.940
How did this archery turn
into shooting in the sky?

20:58.540 --> 21:00.840
Fourth Young Lady,
are you shooting willows

21:00.840 --> 21:01.700
or kites?

21:02.099 --> 21:03.339
My archery isn't great,

21:03.579 --> 21:05.160
and the wind is strong today.

21:05.160 --> 21:06.780
That's why I missed my target.

21:08.980 --> 21:10.460
(I don't want to soar high with you.)

21:16.400 --> 21:18.000
(I prefer shooting you with this arrow.)

21:19.780 --> 21:20.460
Madam,

21:20.659 --> 21:22.540
Zhao usually doesn't practice archery.

21:22.540 --> 21:24.220
I'm not sure
what's gotten into her today.

21:24.740 --> 21:25.339
Ming!

21:25.940 --> 21:27.619
It's some men having some fun.

21:27.740 --> 21:29.680
Why are you trying
to draw attention to yourself?

21:29.680 --> 21:32.120
Women shouldn't even
be learning archery in the first place.

21:34.659 --> 21:35.339
Madam,

21:35.460 --> 21:36.960
why don't we head back to the house

21:36.960 --> 21:38.600
to enjoy some fruit and rest for a bit?

21:38.940 --> 21:39.619
Good idea.

21:54.780 --> 21:55.139
You...

21:57.220 --> 21:58.280
The wind really is strong.

22:00.339 --> 22:01.060
Fourth Young Lady,

22:01.460 --> 22:03.099
am I in trouble?

22:03.579 --> 22:04.899
It's only a kite.

22:05.819 --> 22:07.419
The Marquis won't mind it,

22:08.339 --> 22:08.819
right?

22:13.819 --> 22:14.460
Zhao,

22:15.220 --> 22:17.780
can you teach me
how to release the arrow?

22:19.099 --> 22:20.899
I heard the Marquis of Jining

22:20.899 --> 22:23.099
is famous in the capital
for his archery skills.

22:28.260 --> 22:28.819
I...

22:29.819 --> 22:30.579
Your Lordship.

22:32.460 --> 22:34.659
I wouldn't call myself an expert.

22:35.460 --> 22:37.099
But this little willow-shooting trick

22:37.980 --> 22:39.099
is no challenge for me.

22:43.099 --> 22:44.659
Fifth Young Lady, you see.

22:45.060 --> 22:46.500
To shoot accurately and steadily,

22:46.859 --> 22:49.659
the arrow needs to be exactly
three times the length of its head

22:49.980 --> 22:52.400
and perfectly symmetrical
along all four sides of the shaft.

22:52.400 --> 22:53.840
Only then do you have a steady aim,

22:53.840 --> 22:55.840
achieving what is mentioned
in the Rites of Zhou,

22:55.840 --> 22:59.300
"Even in strong winds,
it will not falter."

23:00.860 --> 23:02.520
You're very knowledgeable,
Your Lordship.

23:02.520 --> 23:03.460
Knowledgeable indeed.

23:03.819 --> 23:05.540
But if you don't shoot soon,

23:05.980 --> 23:07.419
the flowers in the gourd will wither.

23:10.179 --> 23:11.760
Fifth Young Lady, watch this carefully.

23:14.819 --> 23:17.000
Your arm must be steady,
and your mind must be calm.

23:18.260 --> 23:19.940
Aim for the roundest part of the gourd.

23:25.139 --> 23:26.179
Then release the arrow.

23:40.659 --> 23:41.260
This...

23:41.260 --> 23:44.099
It is indeed very windy.

23:45.260 --> 23:46.139
Yes, it sure is.

23:47.819 --> 23:49.339
Do you want to try one more time?

23:52.300 --> 23:53.300
The wind

23:53.980 --> 23:55.440
was indeed strong just now.

23:55.859 --> 23:56.960
I'll try one more time.

24:00.819 --> 24:02.619
Aim for the roundest part of the gourd.

24:03.460 --> 24:04.600
Then release the arrow.

24:09.670 --> 24:12.240
The arrow's fletching is definitely
not made from eagle feathers.

24:12.240 --> 24:13.320
It can't shoot accurately.

24:13.320 --> 24:16.020
The arm must be steady,
and the mind must be calm.

24:17.060 --> 24:18.579
Aim for the roundest part of the gourd.

24:23.819 --> 24:24.339
She hit it!

24:24.619 --> 24:26.419
You truly have remarkable skills.

24:26.740 --> 24:28.940
I learned in one try
and hit the target on my first try

24:28.960 --> 24:30.400
just by following your instructions.

24:31.300 --> 24:32.579
You're a quick learner.

24:34.060 --> 24:35.500
But who picks up archery this fast?

24:35.700 --> 24:37.480
You're already skilled in archery,
right?

24:41.220 --> 24:42.760
(This woman is decent in appearance.)

24:42.859 --> 24:44.240
(But she's brash and sharp-tongued.)

24:44.300 --> 24:46.179
(Why is she so infatuated with me?)

24:46.500 --> 24:47.179
(This won't do.)

24:47.470 --> 24:48.880
(How do I call off this engagement?)

24:48.890 --> 24:50.139
(How do I explain it to Sister?)

24:50.540 --> 24:51.379
(What a headache.)

24:54.220 --> 24:56.120
Madam Wang's words
are too narrow-minded.

24:56.859 --> 24:58.960
Women like Fu Hao
expanded territories in the past

24:58.960 --> 25:00.850
and Mulan
took her father's place in the army.

25:00.980 --> 25:03.160
Today, there's Madam Wa Shi
who suppressed a rebellion

25:03.160 --> 25:04.600
and took over administrative duties.

25:04.600 --> 25:07.060
There's no such thing
as something only men can do

25:07.260 --> 25:08.500
and women cannot in this era.

25:09.379 --> 25:11.220
She says plenty of things
that aren't right.

25:11.899 --> 25:13.260
I won't take any of it to heart.

25:18.360 --> 25:20.440
Mother is going to blame me
for being useless again.

25:21.470 --> 25:23.300
I often hear the ladies
in the capital praise

25:24.640 --> 25:26.700
Fifth Young Lady for being skilled
in the four arts

25:27.060 --> 25:27.740
and needlework.

25:28.460 --> 25:30.740
Seeing you today,
you're even more gentle and dignified.

25:31.270 --> 25:33.920
Women have always been admired
for their gentleness and obedience.

25:33.920 --> 25:35.899
Fifth Young Lady, why belittle yourself?

25:37.139 --> 25:38.260
To Mother,

25:39.859 --> 25:42.700
if my sister can do something
that I can't,

25:43.540 --> 25:44.540
that means I'm useless.

25:46.220 --> 25:47.260
That's too narrow-minded.

25:47.940 --> 25:49.899
It's like this branch and this arrow.

25:51.300 --> 25:52.280
Which is useful,

25:52.899 --> 25:53.780
and which is not?

25:55.339 --> 25:57.260
The arrow can be used in battle.

25:58.379 --> 26:01.940
But what's the use of the branch?

26:03.419 --> 26:05.020
If the branch is on a tree,

26:05.360 --> 26:07.120
it can shield people
from the wind and rain.

26:07.260 --> 26:10.020
The bark can be used to make paper.

26:10.859 --> 26:12.980
Both serve different purposes.

26:13.300 --> 26:14.680
Neither is more or less important.

26:15.220 --> 26:16.500
It's the same with people.

26:32.379 --> 26:33.099
There's a leaf.

26:45.160 --> 26:47.080
Wearing tiger talismans
on Dragon Boat Festival

26:47.179 --> 26:48.880
can ward off evil
and bring good fortune.

26:48.880 --> 26:51.300
These two young ladies
personally embroidered tiger talismans

26:51.300 --> 26:53.020
for you two gentlemen,

26:53.659 --> 26:55.579
hoping to bring a good omen.

26:57.540 --> 26:59.300
The embroidery and inlay work

26:59.500 --> 27:01.220
are both exquisite.

27:01.500 --> 27:02.740
Ming embroidered this one.

27:03.020 --> 27:04.899
Her stitches are delicate.

27:05.500 --> 27:07.419
This one was embroidered by Zhao.

27:07.419 --> 27:08.360
Zhao's embroidery...

27:11.819 --> 27:12.940
Well,

27:14.260 --> 27:15.540
it's still a tiger talisman.

27:15.540 --> 27:16.540
It's quite good as well.

27:17.419 --> 27:19.500
Please accept it, gentlemen.

27:20.659 --> 27:21.419
Thank you, Madam.

27:23.300 --> 27:24.060
Thank you.

27:30.339 --> 27:32.600
(Fourth Young Lady Dou's embroidery
is rather rough.)

27:32.859 --> 27:34.360
(But she still put in a lot of effort)

27:34.360 --> 27:35.800
(to make a tiger talisman for me.)

27:36.300 --> 27:37.859
(It shows how deeply she cares for me.)

27:40.760 --> 27:42.520
(It's a pity
our personalities don't match.)

27:42.520 --> 27:43.740
(I'll have to let her down.)

27:44.619 --> 27:45.940
(But Fifth Young Lady's work...)

27:48.339 --> 27:50.339
(Fourth Young Lady has a unique mind,)

27:50.819 --> 27:52.000
(She's genuine and sincere.)

27:52.220 --> 27:53.800
(Truly rare qualities in this world.)

27:59.179 --> 28:02.179
Our tea plantation in the back hills
has beautiful scenery.

28:02.579 --> 28:04.859
Since this is your first time visiting
our manor,

28:04.940 --> 28:06.020
I've arranged for a servant

28:06.020 --> 28:07.780
to take you both on a stroll there.

28:10.579 --> 28:11.579
Thank you, Madam.

28:14.980 --> 28:17.099
Since we both dislike heat
and prefer quiet,

28:17.300 --> 28:19.260
we'll just head to the pavilion.

28:19.619 --> 28:22.139
Once Zhao and Ming
have prepared the banquet,

28:22.379 --> 28:25.220
we can go straight
to the feast and have drinks.

28:25.980 --> 28:26.880
Please come with me.

28:26.880 --> 28:27.339
All right.

28:28.859 --> 28:29.680
This way, please.

28:41.540 --> 28:42.600
Everything is arranged.

28:42.980 --> 28:44.859
But those things
don't understand human speech.

28:45.099 --> 28:47.339
How can we make them
only go for the Marquis?

28:47.579 --> 28:48.859
What if it goes for Mr. Wu Shan?

28:48.859 --> 28:50.300
They won't make a mistake.

28:50.980 --> 28:52.700
They will definitely go for Wei Tingyu.

28:53.379 --> 28:54.419
I've cleared everyone out.

28:54.619 --> 28:56.619
We can't afford any slip-ups
with Dou Zhao.

28:57.659 --> 28:58.980
After an hour,

28:59.619 --> 29:02.020
I'll bring Madam Wei over.

29:03.260 --> 29:03.899
Yes, Madam.

29:10.540 --> 29:12.060
It's indeed a beautiful scenery.

29:13.940 --> 29:14.899
It's all right, I guess.

29:28.099 --> 29:28.780
Wait, Mr. Wei.

29:31.980 --> 29:32.419
Thank you.

29:35.500 --> 29:36.700
Truly exquisite.

29:37.700 --> 29:40.200
Fifth Young Lady truly has a refined
and thoughtful nature.

29:40.500 --> 29:41.940
Every bead in this design

29:41.940 --> 29:43.460
is clearly crafted with great care.

29:44.360 --> 29:46.640
Well, Fourth Young Lady also put
a lot of thought into it.

29:46.700 --> 29:47.740
But her thinking

29:48.940 --> 29:49.819
is unique.

29:54.819 --> 29:57.619
"The crane calls in the marshes,
the fish lurks in the depths."

29:58.339 --> 29:59.220
If these were reversed,

30:00.020 --> 30:01.220
the crane wouldn't be a crane,

30:01.700 --> 30:03.220
and the fish wouldn't be a fish.

30:04.139 --> 30:05.379
If we could switch them,

30:05.940 --> 30:08.179
wouldn't that be perfect?

30:13.099 --> 30:15.320
This... this is something made
by a young lady

30:15.320 --> 30:16.280
and given by elders.

30:16.280 --> 30:17.480
Exchanging it privately

30:18.300 --> 30:19.320
would be too impolite.

30:20.859 --> 30:22.740
Mr. Wu, I must disagree.

30:23.179 --> 30:25.139
Festive gifts are no big deal.

30:25.819 --> 30:27.780
Besides, can something forced upon us

30:27.780 --> 30:28.880
by elders truly bring joy?

30:30.060 --> 30:30.700
How shallow.

30:33.780 --> 30:34.500
Mr. Wei,

30:34.700 --> 30:36.300
this... this might not be appropriate.

30:37.339 --> 30:38.060
Mr. Wei!

30:48.619 --> 30:50.740
The variety of light and hearty dishes

30:50.860 --> 30:52.040
is still fairly acceptable.

30:54.440 --> 30:56.440
But the cold dishes
shouldn't be served in bowls.

30:56.440 --> 30:57.680
Switch to platters instead.

30:57.780 --> 30:58.720
Yes, Young Lady.

30:59.980 --> 31:02.780
Before serving the duck and barley soup,

31:03.139 --> 31:04.560
make sure to shred the duck meat.

31:04.899 --> 31:05.720
Yes, Young Lady.

31:05.720 --> 31:07.819
Prepare more snowflake pastries.

31:08.099 --> 31:09.619
If anyone doesn't eat cold dishes,

31:09.780 --> 31:11.880
serve them room-temperature
mung bean soup instead.

31:12.099 --> 31:13.960
Entertaining distinguished guests
at a banquet

31:13.960 --> 31:15.320
requires the utmost care.

31:15.379 --> 31:17.139
Zhao, you truly consider every detail.

31:17.540 --> 31:20.179
What do you think
of the fruit-serving dishes I chose?

31:20.500 --> 31:21.339
Are they appropriate?

31:24.859 --> 31:25.579
Fourth Young Lady,

31:25.700 --> 31:26.619
I'm truly sorry.

31:27.659 --> 31:29.419
Why are you so careless?

31:29.700 --> 31:31.099
Luckily, it wasn't anything hot.

31:31.099 --> 31:31.780
Come with me.

31:31.780 --> 31:34.420
Let me attend to Fourth Young Lady
to the side room to get changed.

31:34.420 --> 31:35.000
It's all right.

31:35.010 --> 31:37.250
Let me just get everything ready
for the banquet first.

31:37.260 --> 31:38.460
We have a lot of guests today,

31:38.579 --> 31:40.060
and your dress is quite sheer.

31:40.060 --> 31:41.300
If someone sees you like this,

31:41.300 --> 31:42.780
it could damage your reputation.

31:42.859 --> 31:44.379
It's better if you change first.

31:45.980 --> 31:46.500
Zhao.

31:47.659 --> 31:48.300
Keep preparing.

31:48.300 --> 31:49.680
I'll go and see what's going on.

31:50.579 --> 31:51.700
Your dress is sheer.

31:51.700 --> 31:53.020
What if you catch a cold?

31:53.220 --> 31:54.020
It'll be quick.

31:54.020 --> 31:55.780
It's just ahead. Come on now.

32:02.080 --> 32:03.720
(Dai Jian, Governor of Shengtian)

32:04.619 --> 32:05.659
It's just a small gift.

32:05.980 --> 32:07.579
I hope you'll accept it.

32:15.899 --> 32:18.060
This is quite a generous gift.

32:19.980 --> 32:21.280
Yuanji, you're too generous.

32:21.540 --> 32:23.940
Then I shall accept them.

32:25.780 --> 32:27.280
Send this to the Governor's carriage.

32:27.280 --> 32:27.960
Yes, Master.

32:28.700 --> 32:29.659
Please have a seat.

32:29.899 --> 32:30.339
You, too.

32:30.740 --> 32:31.819
We're almost there.

32:32.179 --> 32:33.700
Why are you in a rush, Nanny Zhou?

32:34.740 --> 32:36.220
The banquet is going to start soon.

32:36.220 --> 32:36.940
We can't delay it.

32:36.950 --> 32:38.160
I'll accompany Zhao.

32:38.160 --> 32:39.340
I can cover a little for her.

32:39.340 --> 32:39.980
No need.

32:42.899 --> 32:44.020
I mean

32:44.020 --> 32:46.020
I can help her get changed.

32:46.590 --> 32:49.360
You don't have to twist my arm
when I want to help her to get changed.

32:50.179 --> 32:51.860
We can attend
to Fourth Young Lady's need.

32:51.860 --> 32:53.660
What are you trying to pull here,
Nanny Zhou?

32:53.660 --> 32:55.240
I'm not. Just helping her to get changed.

32:55.240 --> 32:56.740
You don't allow Dou Ming to follow me.

32:56.740 --> 32:58.139
I want to see

32:58.360 --> 32:59.800
what's waiting for me in this room.

33:10.099 --> 33:10.819
Mr. Wu?

33:10.819 --> 33:12.300
Why is Mr. Wu here?

33:12.310 --> 33:14.320
When Mr. Wu was taking a stroll
in the back hills,

33:14.320 --> 33:16.740
a group of swallowtail butterflies
suddenly chased after him.

33:16.740 --> 33:17.980
After that, he fell unconscious.

33:19.780 --> 33:21.040
Swallowtail butterfly?

33:35.780 --> 33:36.960
Get the physician here quickly

33:37.220 --> 33:38.480
and notify the elders at home.

33:39.179 --> 33:40.370
He is covered in scale powder

33:40.540 --> 33:41.980
and only breaks out in rashes.

33:41.980 --> 33:43.619
No need to let both Masters know.

33:51.819 --> 33:53.850
(The Miluo River is full
of lingering resentment.)

33:53.860 --> 33:54.520
(Wrongfully Killed Man)

33:54.520 --> 33:56.460
(The child was buried
in the southern mountains.)

33:57.600 --> 33:59.320
(Qu Yuan's life ended
in the Miluo River,)

33:59.320 --> 34:00.840
(Wu Shan)
(and today is the Dragon Boat Festival.)

34:00.840 --> 34:02.700
(The poem speaks of early death.)

34:09.980 --> 34:11.000
Still hiding the truth?

34:11.460 --> 34:14.050
You were setting up a situation
where a couple isolated together

34:14.060 --> 34:16.219
to meet while getting changed,
forcing me to marry.

34:16.220 --> 34:19.150
But you didn't expect Wei Tingyu to swap
the tiger talismans with Wu Shan.

34:19.500 --> 34:22.380
For others, the scale powder
only causes redness and itching.

34:22.779 --> 34:24.099
But Wu Shan has a lung condition.

34:24.699 --> 34:26.000
This could cost him his life!

34:26.739 --> 34:28.259
Mr. Wu came to the manor as a guest.

34:28.739 --> 34:30.020
If anything bad happened to him,

34:30.800 --> 34:32.360
how do we explain it to the Wu Family?

34:32.900 --> 34:34.219
Just do as Zhao says.

34:34.699 --> 34:35.340
Yes, Young Lady.

34:39.590 --> 34:40.860
His breathing is getting worse.

34:41.170 --> 34:42.720
There are too many curtains in the room.

34:42.720 --> 34:43.970
The air isn't circulating.

34:43.980 --> 34:46.420
Suxin, go and get someone
to carry him to the yard.

34:46.600 --> 34:48.240
Be gentle and move him carefully.

34:48.240 --> 34:49.540
Then bring me my acupuncture box.

34:49.540 --> 34:50.190
Yes, Young Lady.

34:58.470 --> 35:00.010
Master is hosting guests at the manor.

35:00.020 --> 35:01.150
No one is allowed to disturb.

35:05.299 --> 35:07.020
I, Song Mo, the heir of Duke of Ying,

35:07.699 --> 35:11.259
have come to pay a visit
with gifts for the Dragon Boat Festival!

35:15.420 --> 35:18.579
Now, Grand Secretary Wu
has the final say in the court.

35:18.579 --> 35:19.630
No one can argue with him.

35:20.270 --> 35:22.150
I am of low status
and have little influence.

35:22.579 --> 35:25.340
I truly have no power
to relieve His Majesty's concerns.

35:25.350 --> 35:28.010
The southeast has been hit by a storm,
causing miles of devastation.

35:28.980 --> 35:30.500
While others are avoiding it,

35:31.179 --> 35:33.659
the Dou family wishes
to step into the eye of the storm,

35:33.980 --> 35:35.340
using the wind to their advantage.

35:36.020 --> 35:37.179
Such courage.

35:37.370 --> 35:39.619
Fifth Master, I couldn't stop His Lordship
from entering.

35:43.020 --> 35:45.659
The Dou Family has no connections
with the Duke of Ying.

35:46.139 --> 35:47.940
Since you are here uninvited,

35:48.500 --> 35:49.500
what brings you here?

35:53.139 --> 35:55.779
You sent rice dumplings
to high officials in the capital.

35:56.500 --> 35:59.340
I am curious
about the peculiar filling inside.

36:00.540 --> 36:02.299
So I asked Official Wu for a few to try.

36:11.860 --> 36:13.500
It turns out they're filled with gold.

36:15.060 --> 36:17.699
It seems like Official Wu
has quite a strong prejudice against me.

36:18.060 --> 36:19.900
It's just a regular festival gift.

36:20.420 --> 36:22.659
He can refuse it.

36:23.179 --> 36:25.380
But he actually let you return
it to me in person.

36:25.660 --> 36:27.440
You should put down your weapon,
Lord Song.

36:28.060 --> 36:29.900
From my position
as the Governor of Shengtian,

36:30.659 --> 36:33.420
it looks like you're publicly
threatening an official of the court.

36:34.420 --> 36:35.179
I dare not.

36:40.179 --> 36:41.659
Your Lordship, you…

36:42.779 --> 36:44.900
I have come to inform you respectfully,
Official Dou.

36:45.540 --> 36:48.259
If you still plan to accuse the Duke of Ding
of any crimes,

36:49.179 --> 36:50.740
then I shall offer these rice dumplings

36:51.460 --> 36:52.860
to His Majesty for a taste.

36:56.099 --> 36:59.299
By then, even the Shengtian Prefecture

37:00.300 --> 37:01.579
may not be able to protect you.

37:02.659 --> 37:03.099
You...

37:05.900 --> 37:06.500
Master,

37:06.500 --> 37:07.820
Mr. Wu Shan is unconscious.

37:07.820 --> 37:10.140
Fourth Young Lady has ordered
to carry him to the backyard.

37:10.140 --> 37:10.440
Quiet!

37:10.540 --> 37:11.640
Do not speak recklessly!

37:11.640 --> 37:12.020
Great.

37:12.500 --> 37:14.460
You dare to harm Official Wu's
only grandson!

37:17.420 --> 37:18.380
Preposterous.

37:18.380 --> 37:19.860
Absolutely preposterous!

37:20.139 --> 37:21.820
This is your territory.

37:22.460 --> 37:24.420
If I let him walk around like this,

37:24.579 --> 37:25.940
what would be left of my dignity!

37:26.619 --> 37:27.179
Someone!

37:28.139 --> 37:28.779
You cannot.

37:28.779 --> 37:30.380
Official Dai, don't do it.

37:31.299 --> 37:34.420
You're worried that this marriage
won't be settled anytime soon.

37:34.779 --> 37:35.820
In my opinion,

37:36.179 --> 37:38.659
once fate comes its way,

37:38.980 --> 37:41.099
nothing can stop it.

37:41.500 --> 37:42.480
You're right about that.

37:42.480 --> 37:42.900
Tingzhen!

37:46.900 --> 37:48.060
Why are you here?

37:50.659 --> 37:51.139
Tingzhen,

37:51.860 --> 37:53.460
Mr. Wu is...

37:59.540 --> 38:00.420
Song Mo?

38:14.779 --> 38:15.540
Suxin. Sulan.

38:17.099 --> 38:19.099
Fourth Young Lady, what are you doing?

38:27.660 --> 38:29.099
What are you trying to do to Dezhen?

38:33.440 --> 38:34.960
He has tuberculosis and lung abscesses.

38:34.960 --> 38:36.320
His breathing is getting weaker.

38:36.380 --> 38:38.060
His lungs must be filled with pus now.

38:38.659 --> 38:40.820
Now, he's on the verge of death,
fighting for his life.

38:40.830 --> 38:43.850
I need to perform acupuncture on his Dazhui
and Xuanji acupoints to save him.

38:47.020 --> 38:47.619
Dou Zhao!

38:47.940 --> 38:48.779
How dare you!

38:49.179 --> 38:50.299
In broad daylight,

38:50.310 --> 38:53.150
you and Mr. Wu are tugging at each other
with your clothes in disarray.

38:53.179 --> 38:54.659
What are you trying to do? Get up now!

38:54.770 --> 38:56.450
Mr. Wu Shan's illness flared up
strangely.

38:56.460 --> 38:58.260
Zhao is about
to perform acupuncture on him.

39:01.820 --> 39:04.179
If acupuncture is needed,
it should be done by a physician.

39:04.340 --> 39:05.840
There are rules between men and women.

39:05.840 --> 39:08.140
You have acted in such disgraceful
and improper behavior.

39:08.299 --> 39:11.080
If this gets out, what will happen
to the Dou Family's reputation?

39:11.420 --> 39:11.940
Someone,

39:12.340 --> 39:13.659
quickly help Mr. Wu Shan up.

39:13.980 --> 39:14.739
You're right.

39:17.530 --> 39:19.179
Mother,
saving him is more important now.

39:19.179 --> 39:19.900
Quiet.

39:20.620 --> 39:21.980
Since it's a respiratory condition,

39:22.260 --> 39:23.980
he should be quickly sent
to the physician.

39:23.980 --> 39:25.470
Someone, take him away.

39:25.470 --> 39:27.640
We've already sent someone
to bring the physician here.

39:27.659 --> 39:28.820
But the nearest medical hall

39:28.820 --> 39:29.699
is ten li away.

39:30.179 --> 39:32.619
By the time the physician arrived,
Mr. Wu Shan would be dead.

39:33.370 --> 39:34.750
You've grown up on the battlefield.

39:34.980 --> 39:36.779
So you must know
some injuries and illnesses

39:36.980 --> 39:37.820
cannot be delayed.

39:48.540 --> 39:49.659
Please look into my eyes.

39:50.340 --> 39:52.470
Since you're skilled
in reading facial expressions,

39:52.619 --> 39:53.860
you will know I'm not lying.

39:54.540 --> 39:55.619
I can save him.

40:14.790 --> 40:15.659
You can let go of me.

40:17.699 --> 40:18.500
Hold onto Dezhen.

40:20.619 --> 40:21.020
Lu Zheng,

40:21.420 --> 40:22.860
Bring out all the folding screens

40:23.240 --> 40:24.510
and set them up around tightly.

40:24.520 --> 40:25.310
Yes, Your Lordship.

40:28.099 --> 40:29.460
Everyone, turn around!

40:30.340 --> 40:31.420
If anyone dares to look,

40:33.259 --> 40:34.860
you'll lose your eyes.

40:44.699 --> 40:47.420
Fourth Young Lady,
proceed with the acupuncture now.

40:51.299 --> 40:51.940
Your Lordship,

40:53.139 --> 40:55.579
you openly pointed your blade
at an official of the court.

40:56.299 --> 40:57.500
Do you intend to rebel?

40:58.099 --> 40:59.779
Anyone who stands in my way today

41:01.099 --> 41:01.779
will die.

41:03.450 --> 41:05.619
You've repeatedly tried
to stop me from saving him.

41:05.619 --> 41:06.860
What are your true intentions?

41:07.900 --> 41:08.940
Why do you believe

41:08.940 --> 41:10.340
that this girl can save him?

41:11.139 --> 41:12.299
I trust my judgment.

41:13.179 --> 41:13.820
You...

41:13.980 --> 41:14.699
Lord Song,

41:16.579 --> 41:18.860
you're causing trouble at my place.

41:19.299 --> 41:22.139
Are you forcing me
to bring this matter to the emperor?

41:23.420 --> 41:24.739
I'm sure you know

41:25.179 --> 41:27.619
exactly how Dezhen's illness acted up.

41:28.200 --> 41:29.980
If you want to bring this
before the emperor,

41:30.500 --> 41:33.179
are you prepared
to discard your family's reputation

41:33.860 --> 41:36.299
and the women's honor?

41:41.020 --> 41:41.500
Mother.

41:47.860 --> 41:48.219
Mother.

41:49.179 --> 41:51.820
Dou Zhao, are you trying
to get the entire family killed?

41:52.500 --> 41:54.579
What a clever plan, Lord Song.

41:55.099 --> 41:56.699
If something happened to Mr. Wu,

41:56.980 --> 41:58.659
the emperor would think the Dou Family

41:59.179 --> 42:00.670
is ambitious and power-hungry,

42:00.670 --> 42:03.150
and that we would harm others
because of political differences.

42:03.150 --> 42:04.099
Don't worry, Yuanji.

42:05.020 --> 42:06.150
As the Governor of Shengtian,

42:07.179 --> 42:09.380
I'll testify to this.

42:09.699 --> 42:11.179
Song Mo broke into private property,

42:11.699 --> 42:13.420
threatened a court official
with a blade,

42:13.420 --> 42:14.930
and obstructed efforts to save a life.

42:14.940 --> 42:17.699
Even if this matter reaches the emperor,

42:17.699 --> 42:19.060
the truth will be the same!

42:43.460 --> 42:44.860
This embroidery is quite exquisite.

42:44.870 --> 42:46.950
Fortunately, Song Mo comes
from a military background

42:46.950 --> 42:48.710
and doesn't know
the underhanded tricks.

42:48.720 --> 42:51.050
Otherwise, today would
be a great disaster for the family!

42:51.060 --> 42:51.690
Mind your words.

42:51.700 --> 42:54.050
She is genuinely trying to save you
despite the criticisms.

42:54.050 --> 42:54.860
Are you saying

42:54.860 --> 42:56.860
Fourth Young Lady
also has feelings for me?

42:58.800 --> 43:03.010
♪I lean in and gaze at you
as calm as serene waves♪

43:03.280 --> 43:06.740
♪I'm aware of the vast
and turbulent world♪

43:07.200 --> 43:11.290
♪Moving forward alone,
the expectations of many are hard to bear♪

43:11.770 --> 43:15.520
♪When the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of pride♪

43:15.700 --> 43:18.430
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

43:18.680 --> 43:20.890
♪Or perhaps my heart yearns
for the other side♪

43:20.890 --> 43:23.150
♪Yet there's no place
for me to go in the end♪

43:23.500 --> 43:26.770
♪Your presence by my side
is irreplaceable♪

43:27.130 --> 43:30.350
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

43:30.660 --> 43:34.500
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

43:34.640 --> 43:38.370
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

43:39.110 --> 43:42.270
♪Having you is a blessing♪

43:42.730 --> 43:44.610
♪My heart filled with warmth♪

43:44.930 --> 43:48.460
♪By your side,
I spend the rest of my life♪

43:49.090 --> 43:51.930
♪Your presence by my side
is irreplaceable♪

43:52.770 --> 43:55.880
♪Where my heart yearns
is where I will go♪

43:56.620 --> 43:59.860
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

44:00.360 --> 44:04.030
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

44:04.030 --> 44:08.070
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:08.430 --> 44:11.910
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:12.160 --> 44:15.440
♪Only by being by your side♪

44:15.640 --> 44:20.020
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

44:20.350 --> 44:23.810
♪Until the waves are all spread out♪

44:23.940 --> 44:27.780
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

44:28.150 --> 44:31.140
♪Always together, looking back♪

44:31.750 --> 44:38.750
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

44:48.640 --> 44:49.600
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

44:49.600 --> 44:50.640
(Every medical behavior involved
and medicine used in the drama)

44:50.640 --> 44:51.560
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
